### 5. Get Balance User A
GET {{baseUrl}}/bank/balance/{{userA_Id}}

### 6. Deposit to User A (Triggers 'HIGH_ROLLER' achievement if >= 1000)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bank/deposit
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": "{{userA_Id}}",
    "amount": 1000
}

### 7. Withdraw from User A
POST {{baseUrl}}/bank/withdraw
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": "{{userA_Id}}",
    "amount": 50
}

### 8. Transfer from User A to User B (Triggers 'FIRST_TRANSFER' achievement)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bank/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "fromUserId": "{{userA_Id}}",
    "toUserId": "{{userB_Id}}",
    "amount": 100
}

### 9. Get Statement User A
GET {{baseUrl}}/bank/statement/{{userA_Id}}

### 10. Get Gamification Profile User A (Check XP and Achievements)
GET {{baseUrl}}/gamification/profile/{{userA_Id}}
